  "prompt": "What is nag mani?",
  "response": "Nag Mani, often referred to as \"Naag Mani,\" is a mythical gem or treasure in Indian folklore and Hindu mythology. It is said to be possessed by a naag (snake), specifically a cobra. According to legends, the naag mani has extraordinary powers and can bring immense wealth, health, prosperity, and protection to its owner. \n\nThe concept of nag mani is popular in various stories, songs, and films within Indian culture. While there is no scientific evidence supporting the existence of such a gem, it continues to be a significant and intriguing aspect of mythological narratives and continues to captivate the imagination of many.",
